1
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,880
I've become the Strategist.

2
00:00:26,360 --> 00:00:27,560
What rotten luck.

3
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:36,560
Your clothes are so hard to put on.

4
00:00:36,800 --> 00:00:38,120
What did we do last night?

5
00:00:38,120 --> 00:00:39,320
Yeah, how did we end up swapping clothes?

6
00:00:39,320 --> 00:00:40,600
Yeah, I'm a clean freak, you know.

7
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:42,000
You're a clean freak?

8
00:00:42,040 --> 00:00:43,560
Your clothes... they're rancid.

9
00:00:43,560 --> 00:00:45,240
The stench is blinding me.

10
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:46,000
I can't even open my eyes.

11
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:47,120
Just take them off.

12
00:00:47,120 --> 00:00:48,200
Your clothes are so ugly.

13
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:48,800
Don't touch me.

14
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:49,120
Don't.

15
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:50,800
Stop it.

16
00:00:52,120 --> 00:00:53,680
This is the Lord's favorite thumb ring.

17
00:00:53,680 --> 00:00:54,920
Why is it on your hand?

18
00:00:55,960 --> 00:00:57,600
I really can't pull it off.

19
00:00:57,720 --> 00:00:59,040
It's stuck.

20
00:00:59,160 --> 00:01:00,320
On behalf of the Lord...

21
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:01,040
I'll execute you.

22
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:02,080
Wait, wait, wait. Hold on.

23
00:01:02,760 --> 00:01:03,680
If I'm not mistaken...

24
00:01:03,680 --> 00:01:05,280
isn't that the Lord's sword?

25
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:06,720
Having that sword...

26
00:01:06,720 --> 00:01:08,200
is a much bigger deal than my thumb ring.

27
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:09,360
I...

28
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:10,200
Strategist...

29
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:11,320
are you planning a rebellion?

30
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:13,120
Don't you dare say that!

31
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,320
Last night, someone...

32
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:15,440
tied it to me with a double knot.

33
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,240
Morning, Strategist. Morning, Brother.

34
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:18,000
Qiao.

35
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:18,640
Let me tell you something.

36
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:19,760
The Strategist is planning a rebellion.

37
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:21,680
D-d-don't say such things!

38
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:23,240
What's that in your hand?

39
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:24,840
The Lord's official seal.

40
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,040
This...

41
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,120
What on earth happened here?

42
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,360
I don't remember a thing.

43
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:41,640
That wine gave me such a headache.

44
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:44,840
I think it's coming back to me.

45
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:46,880
Recently,

46
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:49,680
our country and the Daye Kingdom are at a standoff.

47
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,720
But due to blocked river channels,

48
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:52,960
the warships

49
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:54,880
cannot reach the front lines.

50
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:56,000
Therefore,

51
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,800
I have obtained this Divine Dredging Artifact.

52
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:01,280
Legend has it that pouring this artifact into the canal

53
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:02,440
within a month

54
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:03,240
will clear the channel.

55
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,920
Today is the Mid-Autumn Festival.

56
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:07,960
This is fine wine, a tribute from the South.

57
00:02:09,040 --> 00:02:10,520
I invite you all to taste it.

58
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:11,520
As for this artifact,

59
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:12,600
send it to the Treasure Pavilion.

60
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:13,920
Guard it well.

61
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:15,800
Take care, my Lord.

62
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,240
Strategist, what are you doing?

63
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:18,840
You...

64
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:19,880
how can you be so disrespectful?

65
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:20,680
You three,

66
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,320
drink up.

67
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:22,480
There are plenty more jars.

68
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:23,560
Xiaotan,

69
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,520
I'd rather take it home

70
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,600
and enjoy it by myself.

71
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:27,520
Then go ask the Lord.

72
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,360
No, no, no.

73
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:30,800
Drink up. Fine, I'll drink.

74
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,440
Exactly, drink up. Come on.

75
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:33,520
It's just wine, isn't it?

76
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:34,960
Xiaotan, why aren't you drinking?

77
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:35,960
The Lord told you to drink,

78
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:36,720
not me.

79
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,400
Let me toast you.

80
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,360
I hope that before the Lord,

81
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,840
you can put in a good word for us.

82
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:42,360
All right?

83
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,200
Did you drink it?

84
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:44,040
Come on, come on.

85
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:44,800
Strategist,

86
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:46,200
stop st-staring at me.

87
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:47,600
You sissy Strategist.

88
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,520
Lift it up, come on.

89
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:55,520
I can't, brothers.

90
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:57,400
I'm gonna go throw up.

91
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,480
You're useless.

92
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:02,960
Can't hold your liquor, huh?

93
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:03,880
Long.

94
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,680
Keep lifting.

95
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,360
Let's lift it together.

96
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:06,920
Lift!

97
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:07,280
Roll it.

98
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:07,840
Let's go.

99
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,600
Roll it!

100
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:09,240
Come on, let's go.

101
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,000
This way.

102
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:10,720
This way.

103
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:11,600
Over here.

104
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:13,720
Push hard on this side.

105
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,480
Come on.

106
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,240
Come on.

107
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:18,840
Are you sure that's how it was?

108
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:20,680
It must have been.

109
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:21,400
You came in on your own.

110
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,480
It has nothing to do with me.

111
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:23,480
Nothing at all.

112
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:25,480
If I remember correctly,

113
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:26,840
your name is Wei Qiao.

114
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:29,240
Then what's written on that wall?

115
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:55,600
Darn it, darn it.

116
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,480
Is this really going to get our nine clans exterminated?

117
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,920
What are we going to do?

118
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:00,120
What should we do?

119
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:01,960
Strategist.

120
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,040
Why are you so scared?

121
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,280
Is it me?

122
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,880
Why don't I feel anything?

123
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,000
This...

124
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:16,600
This...

125
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:20,280
Why does this smell so muddy?

126
00:04:22,440 --> 00:04:24,200
This is the Divine Dredging Artifact the Lord found.

127
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,480
Why... why is it cracked?

128
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:27,120
This concerns the war effort!

129
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,120
The Lord even said...

130
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,840
...he wanted to escort it personally.

131
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:31,520
This is going to get our nine clans exterminated!

132
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:32,240
This is a serious matter.

133
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,600
I'd better go report to the Lord.

134
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:34,400
Come back!

135
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:35,480
What for?

136
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:40,760
The Lord can't know about this.

137
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:41,600
That's right.

138
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:42,640
Why?

139
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,760
Let's break it down for Qiao from the start.

140
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,000
Look here.

141
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:48,920
I took the Lord's thumb ring.

142
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:49,760
What's the punishment?

143
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:50,640
Just twenty military strokes.

144
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,600
And me taking the Lord's sword?

145
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:53,360
Fifty.

146
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,160
You took the Official seal privately.

147
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:57,360
Beheading.

148
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:58,960
But...

149
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:00,360
...compared to this matter...

150
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,360
...your issue is nothing.

151
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,360
Why?

152
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:03,680
Mine is a mere twenty military strokes.

153
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:04,760
How about for the sake of my brothers...

154
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:05,160
...this matter...

155
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:05,680
...I'll take the blame.

156
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,680
I'm older.

157
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,800
I might not survive fifty military strokes.

158
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:10,440
So this...

159
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:11,160
...I'll take the blame.

160
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:11,920
Strategist...

161
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,000
...you need to take care of your health.

162
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:13,880
What health is there to take care of?

163
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,520
If in the future...

164
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:15,400
...for the sake of you two...

165
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:16,120
...I'm willing to do anything.

166
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:16,920
Strat... Brother!

167
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,760
My two brothers.

168
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:19,760
So loyal.

169
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:22,440
But I'm dead either way.

170
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:23,440
How can I let you take the blame?

171
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:25,640
I'll do it.

172
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:28,000
This kid is so sensible.

173
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:28,640
Righteous.

174
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,640
I know a skilled craftsman in Jingdezhen.

175
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:32,880
He can definitely repair this vat.

176
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:34,560
That works!

177
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:37,520
I'm exhausted.

178
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:40,400
Isn't it all because of you?

179
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:41,880
Qiao came up with such a rotten idea.

180
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:42,600
Didn't you say...

181
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,840
Didn't you say, "You decide, you decide"?

182
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:45,480
That's because... Let's not blame each other.

183
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,400
Unity, unity.

184
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:46,880
By the way.

185
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,120
Big Brother.

186
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,560
Your fiancée is here.

187
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,720
She said she's waiting for you outside the city.

188
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:52,000
You have a fiancée?

189
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:52,640
You actually...

190
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:54,000
Who has a fiancée?

191
00:06:04,880 --> 00:06:05,560
Brother Wei.

192
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,360
Is this love?

193
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:19,960
That is also the poison of love.

194
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,080
I want to be poisoned too.

195
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:26,080
You'll have plenty of chances later.

196
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:28,640
There must be something fishy here.

197
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,000
Let's go meet her.

198
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:31,880
Follow my lead.

199
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:34,880
Xiao Liang is here.

200
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:35,880
Let me introduce you.

201
00:06:35,880 --> 00:06:37,280
My fiancée, Qinqin.

202
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,120
Xiao Liang.

203
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:46,200
Once we're out, won't I be your leader?

204
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:48,040
Did you see that?

205
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:49,920
Something's definitely wrong

206
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:53,320
Does General Wei have some unspeakable secret?

207
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,800
I've been kidnapped

208
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:55,760
What?

209
00:06:56,440 --> 00:06:57,560
Kidnapped by love

210
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:58,480
Get lost

211
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:05,200
Really bad

212
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,560
It really is bad

213
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,520
You mean "Delicacies," right?

214
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,160
Delicacies

215
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:13,720
None of your business

216
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:14,640
You're the one who's shameful

217
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,360
Miss

218
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:17,800
Can we speak in private?

219
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:19,960
I am Aqin

220
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,440
Greetings, Lord Yuwen

221
00:07:21,960 --> 00:07:22,880
Greetings, Miss Aqin

222
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:24,080
May I ask, Miss,

223
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:26,000
when were you betrothed from the womb to General Wei Long?

224
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,360
When I was in my mother's womb

225
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:30,520
When I was in my mother's womb

226
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:32,080
Then why appear now?

227
00:07:32,080 --> 00:07:33,960
First, I have just reached marriageable age

228
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:35,400
Second, our hometown is conscripting soldiers

229
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:36,960
My father is the only male in the family

230
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:37,840
If I do not marry,

231
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:39,400
my father will have to go to war

232
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:40,320
Where is your hometown, Miss?

233
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:42,160
Weijia Village, Xieliang County, Puzhou, Shanxi

234
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,280
Are you neighbors with General Wei?

235
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,160
We are not neighbors

236
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:45,840
General Wei lives in the third house in the east of the village

237
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:47,280
My family lives in the fifth house in the east of the village

238
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:49,280
Then why not be betrothed from the womb to the person in the fourth house?

239
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:50,960
The fourth house is the village latrine

240
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:54,280
Is there a yellow dog and a fool at the village entrance?

241
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:55,640
There used to be a yellow dog at the entrance

242
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:56,480
And a fool

243
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:58,320
But after the fool teased the dog and was bitten,

244
00:07:58,320 --> 00:07:59,080
he died from the wound

245
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:00,520
The fool's family killed the dog in anger

246
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:02,320
Now there is nothing at the village entrance

247
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:05,440
Wei... Wei Long

248
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,760
Is everything she said correct?
